OL,3,CCoroner urges action on road deaths
OL,4,Ccaused by drivers with failing eyesight
OL,6,FAn inquest into the deaths of four
OL,7,Fpeople killed by drivers with failing
OL,8,Feyesight has found enforcement of
OL,9,Fvisual legal standards for motorists
OL,10,Fis "ineffective and unsafe".
OL,12,FHM Senior Coroner for Lancashire Dr
OL,13,FJames Adeley has sent a report to
OL,14,FTransport Secretary Heidi Alexander to
OL,15,Fsay action should be taken to prevent
OL,16,Ffuture deaths.
