OL,3,CCoroner urges action on road deaths
OL,4,Ccaused by drivers with failing eyesight
OL,6,FHe labelled the licensing system for
OL,7,Fdrivers as the "laxest in Europe" as
OL,8,Fhe pointed out the UK was one of only
OL,9,Fthree countries to rely upon self-
OL,10,Freporting of visual conditions
OL,11,Faffecting the ability to drive.
OL,13,FDr Adeley said it was also concerning
OL,14,Fthat the UK was the only European
OL,15,Fcountry to issue licences without any
OL,16,Fvisual checks for a continuous period
OL,17,Fup to the age of 70.
