OL,3,CCoroner urges action on road deaths
OL,4,Ccaused by drivers with failing eyesight
OL,6,FHe made the remarks at the inquests in
OL,7,FPreston of Marie Cunningham, 79, Grace
OL,8,FFoulds, 85, Peter Westwell, 80, and
OL,9,FAnne Ferguson, 75.
OL,11,FFriends Mrs Cunningham and Mrs Foulds
OL,12,Fwere struck by Glyn Jones, 68, in his
OL,13,FAudi A3 as they crossed the road in
OL,14,FSouthport, Merseyside, on November 30
OL,15,F2021.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
