OL,3,CCoroner urges action on road deaths
OL,4,Ccaused by drivers with failing eyesight
OL,6,FJones was aware for some years before
OL,7,Fthe collision that his sight was
OL,8,Finsufficient to meet the minimum
OL,9,Frequirement to drive a car but failed
OL,10,Fto declare it to the Driving and
OL,11,FVehicle Licensing Agency (DVLA).
OL,13,FWhen he was jailed for seven years and
OL,14,Ffour months, his sentencing hearing
OL,15,Fwas told he could not even see his
OL,16,Fsteering wheel clearly.
OL,18,FMr Westwell was hit by Neil Pemberton,
OL,19,F81, as he crossed the road in Langho,
OL,20,Fnear Blackburn, on March 17 2022.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
