OL,3,CCoroner urges action on road deaths
OL,4,Ccaused by drivers with failing eyesight
OL,6,FPemberton, who was jailed for 32
OL,7,Fmonths, had a long history of eye
OL,8,Fdisease and was informed on several
OL,9,Foccasions by different clinicians that
OL,10,Fhe should not drive, the inquest heard.
OL,12,FHe also repeatedly failed to declare
OL,13,Fhis sight deficit on multiple licence
OL,14,Fapplications to the DVLA.
OL,16,FMrs Ferguson died when she was struck
OL,17,Fby a van driven by Vernon Law, 72, in
OL,18,FWhitworth, Rochdale, on July 11 2023.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
