OL,6,FA month before Law was told he had
OL,7,Fcataracts in both eyes but he lied to
OL,8,Fan optometrist that he did not drive.
OL,10,FLaw, who was jailed for four years,
OL,11,Fknew he had problems with his eyes for
OL,12,Fyears before the collision but his
OL,13,Fsight loss could easily have been
OL,14,Fcorrected.
OL,16,FLaw also failed to declare his sight
OL,17,Fissues on multiple licence
OL,18,Fapplications to the DVLA, the inquest
OL,19,Fat County Hall heard.
