OL,3,CCoroner urges action on road deaths
OL,4,Ccaused by drivers with failing eyesight
OL,6,FDr Adeley said: "The four fatalities
OL,7,Fshared the same feature that the
OL,8,Fdriver's sight was well below the
OL,9,Fstandard required to drive a car.
OL,11,F"The current system for 'ensuring'
OL,12,Fdrivers meet the visual legal
OL,13,Fstandards is ineffective, unsafe and
OL,14,Funfit to meet the needs of society as
OL,15,Fevidenced by the deaths of Marie
OL,16,FCunningham, Grace Foulds, Anne
OL,17,FFerguson and Peter Westwell where the
OL,18,FDVLA continued to provide licences to
OL,19,Fdrivers who had failed to meet the
OL,20,Flegal sight requirements."
