OL,3,CCoroner urges action on road deaths
OL,4,Ccaused by drivers with failing eyesight
OL,6,FDr Adeley said: "My condolences are
OL,7,Fand remain with the families who have
OL,8,Flost loved ones due to collisions
OL,9,Fcaused by drivers who prioritised
OL,10,Ftheir own selfish pleasure,
OL,11,Findependence and enjoyment of
OL,12,Fcontinuing to drive a car when each of
OL,13,Fthem knew that their vision was
OL,14,Fdefective and their inability to see
OL,15,Fpedestrians resulted in four deaths."
