OL,3,CCoroner urges action on road deaths
OL,4,Ccaused by drivers with failing eyesight
OL,6,FWhen drivers reach the age of 70, and
OL,7,Fevery three years after, they renew
OL,8,Ftheir licence on the basis of self-
OL,9,Fcertification that they can read a
OL,10,Fnumber plate at 20 metres and have not
OL,11,Fbeen told by a doctor or clinician
OL,12,Fthat their vision has fallen below the
OL,13,Flegal limit for driving.
